.TH SPACEGL_3DVIEW 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_3dview \- SpaceGL OpenGL 3D rendering frontend
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_3dview
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_3dview
is the OpenGL/GLUT/GLEW-based 3D rendering frontend for the SpaceGL engine.
It reads galaxy state from shared memory (SHM) written by
.BR spacegl_server (1)
and renders ships, torpedoes, and galactic objects in real time using
hardware-accelerated OpenGL.
.PP
This binary is typically launched automatically by
.BR spacegl_client (1)
when the
.B gl
argument is specified. It can also be started independently to attach
to an existing shared memory segment.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-version
Print version information and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/bin/spacegl_3dview
OpenGL viewer executable.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_client (1),
.BR spacegl_vulkan (1),
.BR spacegl_server (1)
